**Issue:** Many places have the same boilerplate:
```rust
if let Some(cb) = on_progress {
    cb(SyncProgress::SomeEvent { ... });
}
```

**Suggestion:** Create a helper function:
```rust
fn emit(on_progress: &Option<&ProgressCallback>, event: SyncProgress) {
    if let Some(cb) = on_progress {
        cb(event);
    }
}
```

